name: 透
text: なんか、\nあんまり現実感ないかも
trans:
I kind of, um,
don't feel like I'm in reality just yet.

name: 透
text: プロデューサーの顔見てたら、\nなんかいいことしたかもって感じ、してきた
trans:
When I saw your face,
I did start feeling like I might've just done something good, maybe.

name: プロデューサー
text: いいことだよ\n多くの人にとってもそうだし、何より──
trans:
You sure did!
To a whole lot of people, it was something great, and beyond any of that──

name: プロデューサー
trans: It's something great for you, Toru.

name: 透
text: うちに帰って……\n寝る頃にはさ
trans:
I'll head home...
Bedtime's about now and all.

name: 透
trans: And I'm sure you get it.

name: 透
text: 私にとって、\nきっとすごく大事な日だったって──
trans:
That to me,
this has to have been one of the most important days of my life──
